adient--pale-ocean) !important;}.has-electric-grass-gradient-background{background: var(--wp--preset--gradient--electric-grass) !important;}.has-midnight-gradient-background{background: var(--wp--preset--gradient--midnight) !important;}.has-small-font-size{font-size: var(--wp--preset--font-size--small) !important;}.has-medium-font-size{font-size: var(--wp--preset--font-size--medium) !important;}.has-large-font-size{font-size: var(--wp--preset--font-size--large) !important;}.has-x-large-font-size{font-size: var(--wp--preset--font-size--x-large) !important;}\n/*# sourceURL=global-styles-inline-css */\n</style>\n\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='site-style-css' href='/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/css/style.min_v4.css' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<link rel=\"https://api.w.org/\" href=\"/wp-json/\" /><link rel=\"alternate\" title=\"JSON\" type=\"application/json\" href=\"/wp-json/wp/v2/pages/986\" /><link rel='shortlink' href='/?p=986' />\n<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/common/favicon.svg\">\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/common/apple-touch-icon.png\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"wp-singular page-template page-template-template_recruit_blank page-template-template_recruit_blank-php page page-id-986 page-child parent-pageid-978 wp-theme-custom page-slug-work\">\n<noscript>\n  <div class=\"alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">このページはJavaScriptを使用しています。ご使用中のブラウザはJavaScriptが無効になっているか、JavaScriptに対応していません。<br>JavaScriptを有効にするか、JavaScriptが使用可能なブラウザでアクセスして下さい。</div>\n</noscript>\n<div class=\"site-container\">\n  <header class=\"recruit-header\">\n          <p class=\"recruit-header-logo\"><a class=\"recruit-header-logo__link\" href=\"/recruit\"><img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/common/logo-recruit.svg\" alt=\"アイシーエス　採用サイト\"></a></p>\n        <button class=\"header-menu-button\" id=\"header-menu-button\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon\"><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--top\"></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--bottom\"></span></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-state\">メニュー</span></button>\n    <nav class=\"header-menu\" id=\"header-menu\">\n      <ul class=\"header-nav\">\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/number\">数字で見るICS</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/message\">社長メッセージ</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/work\">仕事を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/people\">人を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/place\">職場を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/info\">募集要項</a></li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"recruit-header-recruit\"> <a class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\"> <span class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button__text\">ENTRY</span></a></p>\n    </nav>\n  </header><main class=\"recruit-main\">\n\t\n<div class=\"recruit-page-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h1 class=\"recruit-page-title\" data-english=\"WORK\"><span class=\"recruit-page-title__text\">仕事を知る</span></h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-page-body\">\n<section>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"row gy-3 justify-content-lg-between\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n<h2 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large lh-1-8\"><span class=\"d-block\">行政・教育・医療など</span><span class=\"d-block\">暮らしが良くなる</span>デジタル社会の実現</h2>\n<p>行政・教育・医療など各分野において、アイシーエスはデジタルとシステムで、暮らしと未来をもっと良くする企業です。<br />暮らしが良くなるデジタル社会の実現に向け、一緒に取り組んでいきましょう。<br />きっと、まだ世の中に存在しない新しい技術を用いることも。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-auto\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/work/img-recruit-work-1.svg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<div class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--gradient pt-0 pb-0\">\n<section>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-protrusion-heading\"><span class=\"d-block d-md-inline\">アイシーエスの</span>キャリアパス</h2>\n<p>基本的にはプログラマーとしてスタートし、徐々に要求定義なども行えるようにシステムエンジニアにキャリアアップしていきます。<br />将来的にはプロジェクトや部署をまとめるリーダーやマネージャーとして。あるいは技術に特化したスペシャリストとして。<br />またはセールスやコンサルに進むケースもあります。<br />アイシーエスの社内制度では自己申告制度が設けられています。<br />自分の得意分野やスキル・興味関心を考えながら、自発的にキャリアパスを歩むことも可能です。</p>\n<picture class=\"d-block text-center\"> <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/work/img-recruit-work-1-pc.svg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" /><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/work/img-recruit-work-1-sp.svg\" alt=\"アイシーエスのキャリアパスの図\" /> </picture>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline mt-120\">ロールモデル</h3>\n<p>入社して２か月程度は、新入社員研修としてプログラムの学習およびプロジェクト演習を行います。<br />新人として配属される際に、新入社員一人に一人ずつ先輩社員がサポート役として付きます。<br />先輩社員に支えてもらいながら、アイシーエス生活がスタートします。<br />少しずつ着実にステップアップしていきましょう。</p>\n<picture class=\"d-block text-center mt-80\"> <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/work/img-recruit-work-2-pc.svg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" /><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/work/img-recruit-work-2-sp.svg\" alt=\"ロールモデルの図\" /> </picture></div>\n</section>\n<div class=\"recruit-page-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\"><nav role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"現在位置\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\"><li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"/\">ホーム</a></li>  <li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"/recruit\">採用サイトトップ</a></li>  <li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\" aria-current=\"page\">仕事を知る</li></ol></nav></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</main>\n\n        <footer class=\"recruit-footer\">\n                            <h2 class=\"recruit-footer-entry-heading\">募集要項</h2>\n                <ul class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list\">\n                    <li class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list__item\"><a class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link\" href=\"/recruit/info\"> <span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__text\">新卒採用</span><span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__arrow\"></span></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list__item\"><a class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link\" href=\"/recruit/info?tab-id=recruit-info-tab&tab-target-id=recruit-info-mid-career-tab-pane\"> <span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__text\">中途採用</span><span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__arrow\"></span></a></li>\n                </ul>\n                        <div class=\"recruit-footer-bottom\"> \n                <p class=\"recruit-footer-bottom-logo\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom//assets/img/recruit/common/logo-recruit-footer.svg\" alt=\"アイシーエス　採用サイト\"></p>\n                <p class=\"recruit-footer-bottom-copyright\">© ICS Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <script type=\"speculationrules\">\n{\"prefetch\":[{\"source\":\"document\",\"where\":{\"and\":[{\"href_matches\":\"/*\"},{\"not\":{\"href_matches\":[\"/ics_cms/wp-*.php\",\"/ics_cms/wp-admin/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/plugins/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/*\",\"/*\\\\?(.+)\"]}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\"a[rel~=\\\"nofollow\\\"]\"}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\".no-prefetch, .no-prefetch a\"}}]},\"eagerness\":\"conservative\"}]}\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/js/libs/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\" id=\"site-bootstrap-js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/js/common.js\" id=\"site-common-js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/plugins/page-links-to/dist/new-tab.js\" id=\"page-links-to-js\"></script>\n  </body>\n</html>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.ics.co.jp/recruit/work","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-24T00:02:28.184Z"}